doctest = true
bench = true

[package]
name = "subscription"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4"
chrono = "0.4.15"
config = "0.13"
tracing-actix-web = "0.5"
tracing-bunyan-formatter = "0.3"
tracing-log = "0.1"

[dependencies.secrecy]
version = "0.8"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6.0"
features = ["runtime-actix-rustls", "macros", "postgres", "uuid", "chrono", "migrate"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
features = ["log"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["registry", "env-filter"]
optional = false

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.1.2"
features = ["v4"]
optional = false

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1"
reqwest = "0.11"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []
